articles.title: $5m lost in scams; 239 people under police probe
articles.content: A total of 239 people are assisting with police investigations over their suspected involvement in scams where victims reportedly lost around $5 million. The cases involve: e-commence scams; friend impersonation scams; job scams; government official impersonation scams; investment scams; and rental scams
